<title>SAFE WITHIN THE VAIL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I malam ah gam a um hi,
 Mun nuom leh gam hingzing chuh;
 Ziechun tui hing chuh a luong zing,
 Van mite lenna munah.

[V2]
 Suongpi, tuilien lau puong ka,
 Luigal kumsawt mun a chun;
 Thikdet khie'n lawngpuon ziel ka,
 Mun galmuong chuh ka tun tieng.

[V3]
 2. Malam zuona kuong tawl zelin,
 Ngaihtak te'n khut in ei sam;
 Pathien kingkang gihawih ngaiin,
 Kumsawt mite tum git chuh.

[V4]
 3. Thikdet khie'n, kuong sunga chuongin,
 Tuipi nem, tawilo chungah;
 Lui lai lamah tuihat kinawk,
 Luipang mun vak chuh nusie'n.

[V5]
 4. Thepna cheng I pelhthak tieng leh,
 Damsung huihpi a beih tieng;
 Hukdamna Suongpi pakchai tiu,
 Van In nuom ei tunpa chuh.</lyrics>
</song>